Home > Music > Drake Brings Out Nicki Minaj In Paris Drake Brings Out Nicki Minaj In Paris 0 0 Posted by Danny Schwartz , Mar 12, 2017 at 07:27pm Watch Nicki Minaj perform "No Frauds," "Only," "Truffle Butter," & "Moment For Life" with Drake. 
Between her provocative and titillating outfit at Paris Fashion Week and the release of her Remy Ma diss "No Frauds," Nicki Minaj has had one of the most eventful weeks of her entire career. She capped it off Sunday night by making an appearance at Drake 's Boy Meets World show in Paris. 
She stayed on stage long enough to join Drake for four songs: "No Frauds," "Only," "Truffle Butter," & "Moment For Life."
